      "gloss_en_full": "A herbivorous, non-ruminant mammal belonging to the even-toed ungulates and pachyderms, found in herds in and around standing and slow-flowing inland waters of sub-Saharan Africa. It has brownish skin, a nearly hairless and massive body, short sturdy legs with webbed toes, a broad head with small eyes and ears, and an enormous mouth with long tusk-like canine teeth (Hippopotamus amphibius).",
